{"id":266,"date":"2017-07-25T17:01:38","date_gmt":"2017-07-25T17:01:38","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/hoodbuilder.dev\/?page_id=266"},"modified":"2023-11-19T04:22:02","modified_gmt":"2023-11-19T04:22:02","slug":"buckeye","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/fire-suppression-systems\/buckeye\/","title":{"rendered":"Buckeye"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1500556319702{background-color: #eeeeec !important;}&#8221;][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-offset-2 vc_col-lg-8 vc_col-md-offset-1 vc_col-md-10&#8243;]<div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e553a6e079\" data-id=\"685e553a6e079\" data-height=\"90\" data-height-mobile=\"70\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"70\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div>[vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"big-para-blue\">To help prevent and stop fires when they occur, Hood Builder recommends Buckeye, a top-of-the-line fire suppression system unlike any other.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text]<div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e553a6e08f\" data-id=\"685e553a6e08f\" data-height=\"60\" data-height-mobile=\"40\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"40\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column]<div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e553a6e09b\" data-id=\"685e553a6e09b\" data-height=\"90\" data-height-mobile=\"70\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"70\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div>[\/vc_column][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-7 vc_col-md-7&#8243;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h4>Buckeye Fire Suppression System<\/h4>\n<p>In a commercial kitchen, it is not unusual to see red-hot cooking surfaces, grease-laden surroundings, and open flames. The combination of these elements is a recipe for a fire outbreak. Fire spreads fast in a kitchen area and must be contained before irreversible damage is done.<\/p>\n<p>To help prevent and stop fires when they occur, Hood Builder recommends Buckeye, a top-of-the-line fire suppression system unlike any other.<\/p>\n<h4>The Buckeye Kitchen Mister\u2122 System.<\/h4>\n<p>This system uses misting technology to suppress fires. Kitchen misters are the most effective firefighting system in the world. They kill fires quickly so they don\u2019t spread, even in grease-laden environments.<\/p>\n<h4>Buckeye System Cylinders<\/h4>\n<p>These fire suppression systems come in BFR-5, BFR-10, BFR-15 and BFR-20 cylinders models and are designated by flow point capacity. You can recharge in 5 and 10 flow point containers so there are no room for mistakes.<\/p>\n<h4>Kitchen Mister Shielded Cable<\/h4>\n<p>Buckeye is listed and approved by the following:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Underwriters Laboratories, Inc. (Standard UL-300)<\/li>\n<li>Underwriters Laboratories of Canada, Inc.<\/li>\n<li>Approved by the New York City Fire Department COA #5550<\/li>\n<li>Complies with NFPA-96 and NFPA-17A Standards<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Full-Service Fire Suppression Maintenance<\/h4>\n<p>You never know when your fire suppression system may malfunction. Don\u2019t allow that to happen. Instead, call us for regular fire system inspections. We\u2019ll make sure your systems operate when needed to prevent loss of life, injury, or property damage.<\/p>\n<p>We can also maintain your systems so that they are ready at a moment\u2019s notice. And if one of your systems breaks down, we\u2019ll be there in a flash to conduct the necessary repairs.<\/p>\n<p>For over 25 years, we have been providing restaurants like yours with the best fire suppression systems on the market. Get Buckeye today and keep your kitchen, personnel, and customers safe.<\/p>\n<p><strong>For a full and fast price quote, contact Hood Builder today at <a href=\"tel:+1-303-777-7720\">303-777-7720<\/a>.<\/strong>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-offset-1 vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-offset-1 vc_col-md-4&#8243;][vc_wp_custommenu nav_menu=&#8221;14&#8243; el_class=&#8221;wps-sidebar-related-links&#8221; title=&#8221;Related Links&#8221;]<div class=\"templatera_shortcode\"><div id=\"\" class=\"wps-row-container vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\" ><div class=\"container wps-vc-container\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner \"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div\n        class=\"sidebar-widget-button-wrap \">\n    <div class=\"sidebar-widget-button\">\n        <a href=\"\/services\/restaurant-services\/\" title=\"Restaurant Services\">\n\n            <div id=\"wps-sidebar-btn-582262\" class=\"sidebar-widget-button-details\">\n                <div class=\"sidebar-widget-button-text\">\n                    <p>Restaurant Services<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n                <div class=\"sidebar-widget-arrow\">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/wp-content\/themes\/wps-hoodbuilder\/assets\/images\/icon-arrow-sidebar-services.svg\" alt=\"\">\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/a>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div\n        class=\"sidebar-widget-button-wrap \">\n    <div class=\"sidebar-widget-button\">\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/fire-suppression-systems\/\" title=\"Fire Protection\">\n\n            <div id=\"wps-sidebar-btn-447920\" class=\"sidebar-widget-button-details\">\n                <div class=\"sidebar-widget-button-text\">\n                    <p>Fire Protection<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n                <div class=\"sidebar-widget-arrow\">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/wp-content\/themes\/wps-hoodbuilder\/assets\/images\/icon-arrow-sidebar-services.svg\" alt=\"\">\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/a>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div\n        class=\"sideb